# Runtime-health artifacts — regenerated by `npm run gallery:runtime` / `gate:ui`.
# Unlike the web workspace (which commits RUNTIME_FINDINGS.md as a stable
# snapshot), BOTH files are ignored here: the desktop gallery renders web-
# workspace page modules cross-workspace, so vite serves them via `@fs/<abs-path>`
# URLs that leak the machine's checkout path into the report — not portable to
# commit. The gate reads the .jsonl in-process; regenerate locally as needed.
src/dev/gallery/RUNTIME_FINDINGS.jsonl
src/dev/gallery/RUNTIME_FINDINGS.md
